SECURITY REQUIREMENTS 

1. Voter Confidentiality (Cryptography)
2. Vote Integrity
3. Voting system availablity and DDOS resilience 
4. Non Repudiation and Digital Signatures
5. Incident Response and Disaster Recovery
6. Voter Authentication
7. Role Based Access Control
8. Scalability and Performance of the voting system
9. Auditability and Immutable Logging
10. Vote Verifiability
11. 24*7 SOC support for Monitoring and Detection
12. Security patch management 
13. Accessibility and Transparency
14. Physical and endpoint security for polling terminals
15. Geolocation Restrictions for Overseas Voting
16. Third-Party Security Audits and Certification
17. Insider Threat Detection and Mitigation
18. Legal Compliance Safeguards
19. Adaptive Threat Intelligence Integration
20. Voter Education and Security Awareness
21. Metadata Anonymisation and Traffic Camouflage
22. Coercion Resistance and Safe Ballot Revocation
23. Self Healing Cybersecurity Architecture
24. Secure Remote Voting Environment (Sandbox)
25. Secure Ballot Deletion Post Election
